      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
