      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>dried oregano</strong> to the pan with your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, preheat the grill to high</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1673366611600-x200.jpg",
