          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1673366611600-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> to the pan with the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 7-8 min further or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>tomato pasta sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1673366614837-x200.jpg",
