            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, transfer the <strong>drained macaroni</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tomato pasta sauce</strong> and mix it all together</p><p>Top with the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong>, <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong> and <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Put the dish under the grill for 8-10 min or until all the cheese is melted and golden – this is your <strong>cheesy tomato macaroni bake</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
